### Send workspace invite
POST http://localhost:6767/invite
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "workspace": "WORKSPACE_ID_HERE",
    "email": "friend@gmail.com",
    "role": "MEMBER"
}

###

### Get all pending invites for workspace
GET http://localhost:6767/invite?workspace=WORKSPACE_ID_HERE

###

### Accept invite via token
POST http://localhost:6767/invite/accept/INVITE_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Decline invite via token
POST http://localhost:6767/invite/decline/INVITE_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Resend invite
POST http://localhost:6767/invite/INVITE_ID_HERE/resend

###

### Cancel/delete invite
DELETE http://localhost:6767/invite/INVITE_ID_HERE
